Dining & Entertainment Rewards
Dining & Entertainment Rewards

Eat ▶ Play

 

Everyday  Rewards

Spend HK$200 or more at designated dining merchants using electronic payments on the same day.

 

From September 5 to September 15:

Get HK$30 dining voucher.

 

From September 16 to September 30:

Get HK$30 Chinese dining voucher

(50 quota before 6 PM; 50 quota available after 6 PM).

 

Monday to Thursday After 6 PM:

Extra Reward:

20 play tokens for APELAND (50 quota available after 6 PM).

 

Buy ▶ Play

Every Friday to Sunday and on public holidays,

Spend HK$1,000 or more at any merchant in the plaza using electronic payments*

Get dining & entertainment: HK$30 dining voucher + HK$30 Chinese dining voucher + 20 play tokens for APELAND (30 packages available daily).

 

*There is no limit on the number of invoices, but each invoice must be for HK$100 or more.
